Welcome to the AmigaGuide documentation for @{b}HWUpdate@{ub}.

You can pick up the latest version by calling 519-672-5568 and typing
HWUPDATE at the JamMail prompt.

A UUCP/NNTP "ACTIVE" file looks like this: 

  comp.sys.amiga.advocacy 108160 108069 n 
  comp.sys.hp48 27444 27357 n
  alt.folklore.computers 84459 84368 n
  comp.sys.amiga.reviews 652 638 n

If you don't recognize this, or if you don't have CNet/3, delete 
@{b}HWUpdate@{ub} right now.

