Program history
***************

     Version 1.0
     -----------
     Initial release ready on 941124.


     Version 1.1
     -----------
     As per a request by Michale Worley, I have changed the search system
     to also match subboards which CONTAIN the newsgroup name, instead of 
     being exactly the same. Released 941125.

     Version 1.2
     -----------
     Changed the search method yet again.  HWUpdate now builds the newsgroup
     name from the Part0/CDROM path.  Added smarter updating and FORCE 
     option.  Released 941207.

     Version 1.21
     ------------
     Fixed a few bugs... One potential Enforcer hit, and a prolem with 
     really long basenames. Released 941209.

     Version 2.0
     -----------
     A complete re-write.  With the help of some of my friends on IRC, 
     HWUpdate is now a completely functional program.  CNet no longer
     needs to be re-loaded after HWUpdate is run.  Fixed some major
     problems, and updated the user interface.  Released 950313.

     Version 2.1
     -----------
     Two MAJOR problems!  First, the newsgroup names were being tested
     case-senstively.  Fixed.  Also, there was a MAJOR error in the
     docuemntation.  It was suggested that HWUpdate be run right before
     IUUNEWS... It should be run right before the mail-run!

@EndNode
